800
00:49:06,372 --> 00:49:08,262
Anda dipanggil
kantor bimbingan, Jay.

801
00:49:08,287 --> 00:49:09,287
Aku?

802
00:49:09,312 --> 00:49:11,115
- Ya.
- Hah?

803
00:49:11,513 --> 00:49:12,513
Itulah yang mereka katakan.

804
00:49:35,579 --> 00:49:36,622
Selamat pagi.

805
00:49:37,259 --> 00:49:39,151
- Silakan duduk.
- Anda memanggil saya, Bu?

806
00:49:39,151 --> 00:49:40,602
Ya, tunggu.

807
